Guide.Content:
Collect cassettes - in the 1st chapter of the game, you will come across several cassettes. Some of them are story-related, others can be found while traveling through the factory. Thanks to them you can learn more about the story and this mysterious place;
Focus on the surroundings - Playtime is a fairly transparent game in which you only have to carefully observe the surroundings. The points you have to go to are quite clearly shown, e.g. they glow in a specific color. Things that are important are hard to miss in this game;
Take your time - you really dont have to hurry. Explore, look around, see what you can do. Nothing will start to chase you unless you perform specific interactions first.
